INSTALL
-------
1) Create a build directory

     mkdir build

2) Change to build directory

     cd build

3) Run cmake, to specify C and Fortran compilers use CC and FC environment
variables, to specify installation prefix use -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:

     CC=gcc FC=gfortran cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt/xdrfile ..

4) Compile

     make

5) Install into specified prefix directory

     make install OR sudo make install
